caption.p: Flow cytometry analysis of the expression of cell surface markers protein in SPFP-MSCs from three OA patients. Cell cultures were positive for the MSC specific markers ( A) CD29 = 92.30 ± 3.20%, ( B) CD73 = 90.91 ± 2.73%, and ( C) CD105 = 83.52 ± 3.23%. and negative for the hematopoietic stem cell markers ( D) CD 34 = 1.04 ± 2.88% and ( E) CD45 = 0.92 ± 1.08%.
